{"tid":1543392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 將重心放係班狗度","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T19:27:00.000Z","uid":286249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc09590d519e3d6244ea22d487e5260f2370107","tid":1543392,"uid":286249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"可能有啲長，俾啲耐性睇晒唔該。<br />\n依加林鄭條八婆玩言語偽術話「撒回」，又大力國際性地宣揚岀去。等班外國人個個以為香港人已經成功咗！<br />\n依加五大訴求，缺一不可呀！！！<br />\n <br />\n屌你老味！我地點都唔可以袋住先！！！<br />\n講跟住落嚟要點做之前，我首先分析下點解今次林鄭會讓半步<br />\n  <br />\n因為全球都關注緊依件事！<br />\n國際文宣做得好！！！文宣組手足做到嘢！！全世界都知道我地爭取緊啲咩。無論中共想點對付香港都要三思而行，因為全世界都望住我地同中共！中共冇得再進一步，所以今次以退為進。<br />\n <br />\n之前係各個國家登報，引起全世界關注。佢地清楚香港人嘅訴求就係撒回修例。所以我地得到大多數人嘅支持！<br />\n <br />\n咁依加點？<br />\n林鄭對外聲稱「撒回」，暫且唔理有冇法律效力先。<br />\n如果我地再衝擊係佢地眼中就會成為「暴徒」。（唔係分化緊，咪屌住）<br />\n所以有好幾個post都話先和理非 &mdash; 死線 &mdash; 最後勇武岀場。大家討論過嘅嘢我就唔浪費口水重複喇。<br />\n  <br />\n跟住落嚟係重點！！！！！！<br />\n  <br />\n我地要大大力還擊林鄭！<br />\n各位巴絲打，特別係文宣組注意！<br />\n <br />\n將黑警嘅暴行放大再放大！<br />\n大大聲咁話俾全世界知：香港警犬到底有幾癲！！！周街亂咬人！<br />\n話俾全世界知成立獨立調查委員會嘅重要性！<br />\n等全世界再次企係香港人依一邊！<br />\n  <br />\n將重心放落香港警犬度！！<br />\n無論大小事都要宣傳！<br />\n話俾全世界知香港警察點樣打到示威者或者普通市民流晒血。所有大事都要講！<br />\n <br />\n唔單止咁！我地要將小事都放大！<br />\n普普通通屌班狗兩句就俾佢地打幾棍同拘捕。所有事都要放大十倍去做外國文宣！<br />\n <br />\n注意一點：必須要已FC！！必須！必須！必須！<br />\n <br />\n一，要令外國人企係我地依一邊，令佢地知道件事未解決！<br />\n二，咁做唔單止係針對外國人士嘅策略，亦都針對班中立同淺黃嘅香港人。<br />\n三，等全世界都鄙視班狗。佢地愈大壓力，就愈易岀錯，佢地愈錯我地贏嘅機會就愈大。<br />\n <br />\n歡迎各位兄弟姐妹嚟理性討論！！<br />\n如果可行嘅話，眾湊多次，幫班狗上報！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  <br />\n記住呀！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n我地有勇亦要有謀！"},{"pid":"44a8bf6cbb9d459dbe0cb729e62907b3426e3e9e","tid":1543392,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c065f8b641f98a39a824e0056d62a7bdf89b35f8","tid":1543392,"uid":21424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s5.ezgif.com/save/ezgif-5-2a08538c8047.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs5.ezgif.com%2Fsave%2Fezgif-5-2a08538c8047.gif&h=0b45625d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f6138c704629dd2b40a98403d330574d2a49baf","tid":1543392,"uid":286249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"a888bcd975595d2bccebfa29ba4f6e8bd09ccfd4","tid":1543392,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"497a2daac4171b6b4c47fc3d5d9df8faadc7ece7","tid":1543392,"uid":286249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫班狗岀名！"},{"pid":"4a139f9fdbd6f481d17017fb26119e306723532e","tid":1543392,"uid":286249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f7a6e596b6d134ffda63a74347109dc25709b7","tid":1543392,"uid":286249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ee3298f02d42ec3ac557939559e5a760516d33